   Plastic-Free Shipping
   Our plastic-free promise. We take our shipping materials seriously;
   made from only recycled materials and end of life must be recyclable
   and/or compostable. What you'll find - simple kraft paper, cardboard
   boxes/envelopes and paper tape!
   Need Help?
   Finding the perfect bar is the first step! Shoot us a note, we're happy
   to provide a product recommendation or answer questions.
   No Returns
   Yes, you read that correctly, we don't accept returns! At the core of
   our business decisions is the environmental impact. Reverse shipping
   contributes to over 5 billion pounds of landfill waste annually:
   research, avoid impulse purchases and ask questions, we're here to
   help!
